      • project

        public Buffer project(ICoordTrans coordTrans,
                      Extent extent,
                      int width,
                      int height)
               throws WarpException
        Description copied from interface: Buffer
        Project buffer using the coordinate transformation. Coordinate transformation has to define the tranformation between target buffer to source buffer. Result buffer will have extent, width and height received as parameters. If coordinate transform is null, transformation will not be applied and result buffer will have the same data but the extent and size of buffer will be modified.
        Specified by:
        project in interface Buffer
        Parameters:
        coordTrans - Coordinate transformation to warp buffer
        extent - Extent of projected buffer
        width - Width of projected buffer
        height - Height of projected buffer
        Returns:
        buffer Buffer projected with extent, width and height received as parameter.
        Throws:
        WarpException - If there are any problem wrapping buffer.
